1
00:01:36,960 --> 00:01:40,120
[Born to Be Alive]

2
00:01:40,140 --> 00:01:43,140
[Episode 36]

3
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,259
If he doesn't like them,

4
00:01:44,259 --> 00:01:45,009
why bother?

5
00:01:45,170 --> 00:01:45,930
It's still a token

6
00:01:45,930 --> 00:01:46,930
of our regard.

7
00:01:47,979 --> 00:01:50,160
These hardcover
Four Great Classical Novels

8
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:51,630
can't be bought abroad.

9
00:01:55,539 --> 00:01:56,800
I'm going out for a bit.

10
00:01:58,080 --> 00:01:58,810
If you drink,

11
00:01:58,840 --> 00:01:59,880
remember to call me to pick you up.

12
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:00,370
I won't drink.

13
00:02:00,370 --> 00:02:01,370
I'll be back soon.

14
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:48,250
The chemical plant owner

15
00:02:48,250 --> 00:02:49,510
has been taken care of.

16
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:51,890
Don't worry.

17
00:02:52,910 --> 00:02:53,990
He won't talk.

18
00:02:55,020 --> 00:02:55,570
Good.

19
00:02:56,890 --> 00:02:58,750
You really have a way with things.

20
00:02:58,990 --> 00:03:00,610
That diversionary tactic

21
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,380
worked perfectly.

22
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,980
Small cost, great results.

23
00:03:05,740 --> 00:03:08,000
The inspection team didn't come in vain,

24
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:10,720
and they can report back successfully.

25
00:03:11,210 --> 00:03:12,540
Those apartments of mine in the south,

26
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:13,870
sell them immediately.

27
00:03:14,460 --> 00:03:15,460
Forget the price.

28
00:03:15,690 --> 00:03:17,290
Sell to anyone who's buying.

29
00:03:17,990 --> 00:03:18,680
Transfer all the money

30
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,950
to Jianshe.

31
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:23,930
What do you mean by this?

32
00:03:26,670 --> 00:03:27,930
It's time to pull back.

33
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:31,640
We can't spread ourselves too thin.

34
00:03:32,260 --> 00:03:33,100
This time,

35
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,430
we managed to deal with

36
00:03:35,430 --> 00:03:36,630
the inspection team.

37
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,300
But if

38
00:03:38,750 --> 00:03:39,380
they suddenly

39
00:03:39,380 --> 00:03:40,640
come back for a review,

40
00:03:41,440 --> 00:03:42,340
we'll be caught

41
00:03:42,370 --> 00:03:43,329
off guard again.

42
00:03:44,380 --> 00:03:45,600
It's a blind spot.

43
00:03:46,310 --> 00:03:47,090
Now is exactly the time

44
00:03:47,090 --> 00:03:48,200
to forge ahead.

45
00:03:48,220 --> 00:03:50,079
We should quit while we're ahead.

46
00:03:52,329 --> 00:03:52,910
After all these years,

47
00:03:52,910 --> 00:03:54,130
we've made enough.

48
00:03:56,460 --> 00:03:57,840
Let's quit while the going is good.

49
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,570
I can't quit.

50
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,690
At the mines right now,

51
00:04:03,690 --> 00:04:04,880
there are still 400,000 tons

52
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,280
of outcrop coal piled up.

53
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:08,440
It's worth at least 200 million.

54
00:04:09,380 --> 00:04:10,600
If we stop now,

55
00:04:11,110 --> 00:04:13,240
we're throwing that 200 million away.

56
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,630
And at Mine No. 2,

57
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:15,550
the proven reserves

58
00:04:15,550 --> 00:04:17,010
are still 10 million tons.

59
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:19,839
I'm not leaving until I've mined it all.

60
00:04:21,100 --> 00:04:21,850
So,

61
00:04:22,770 --> 00:04:23,510
Lin,

62
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:26,220
give me 2 more years.

63
00:04:26,340 --> 00:04:27,220
Just 2 years.

64
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,480
Within 2 years,

65
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:30,330
I'll make a big show
of the regreening efforts

66
00:04:30,330 --> 00:04:31,420
to cooperate with you.

67
00:04:31,420 --> 00:04:32,820
Whoever comes to inspect or interview,

68
00:04:32,820 --> 00:04:33,670
there will be no problem.

69
00:04:33,670 --> 00:04:35,000
I'll shut them all up.

70
00:04:36,610 --> 00:04:38,610
But you have to let me finish mining.

71
00:04:39,170 --> 00:04:40,110
Impossible.

72
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,690
Where are you going?

73
00:04:44,440 --> 00:04:45,290
Impossible!

74
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:46,730
I'm retiring next year.

75
00:04:46,870 --> 00:04:48,200
I want a safe landing!

76
00:04:48,220 --> 00:04:49,280
Do you understand?

77
00:04:50,980 --> 00:04:52,580
Let me tell you, Feng Keqing.

78
00:04:52,940 --> 00:04:54,670
If you can't cooperate with me,

79
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:57,570
I can't protect you.

80
00:05:01,150 --> 00:05:02,180
You protect me?

81
00:05:04,650 --> 00:05:05,390
Lin.

82
00:05:07,820 --> 00:05:09,350
I'm the one protecting you.

83
00:05:12,220 --> 00:05:13,350
Are you crazy?

84
00:05:14,980 --> 00:05:15,910
What do you mean?

85
00:05:20,740 --> 00:05:21,600
Now you want

86
00:05:21,620 --> 00:05:22,970
to just walk away?

87
00:05:27,740 --> 00:05:28,790
It's too late.

88
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:46,659
Mrs. Lin,

89
00:05:47,090 --> 00:05:48,640
I'm here to mooch a meal again.

90
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:49,909
I feel quite bad about it,

91
00:05:49,909 --> 00:05:51,100
so I brought a small gift.

92
00:05:51,100 --> 00:05:51,740
Look at you,

93
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:53,180
you're always so polite.

94
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,280
Come on in.

95
00:05:54,310 --> 00:05:54,980
Lin is home.

96
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,659
Let me do it.

97
00:05:56,690 --> 00:05:57,700
Go have tea with Lin.

98
00:05:57,700 --> 00:05:58,790
You haven't seen him in a while.

99
00:05:58,790 --> 00:05:59,340
Go on.

100
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,270
Lin.

101
00:06:06,210 --> 00:06:07,080
This wine,

102
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:08,150
I have to say,

103
00:06:08,150 --> 00:06:09,060
is actually quite good.

104
00:06:09,060 --> 00:06:09,920
Come, sit down.

105
00:06:11,990 --> 00:06:12,650
Feng.

106
00:06:13,420 --> 00:06:15,190
It's all thanks to you

107
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,870
that Jianshe got to go abroad.

108
00:06:16,870 --> 00:06:18,600
He's adapting well over there.

109
00:06:18,930 --> 00:06:19,780
He said there are

110
00:06:19,780 --> 00:06:21,510
many Chinese people at school.

111
00:06:22,080 --> 00:06:23,840
I have many friends abroad.

112
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:25,240
It's no trouble at all.

113
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,600
In a while,

114
00:06:26,630 --> 00:06:27,530
won't the grandparents

115
00:06:27,530 --> 00:06:28,710
want to go visit him?

116
00:06:30,330 --> 00:06:30,860
When the time comes,

117
00:06:30,860 --> 00:06:32,530
I'll accompany them to get their visas.

118
00:06:32,530 --> 00:06:33,850
Thank you. Thank you.

119
00:06:35,110 --> 00:06:36,000
This time,

120
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:37,420
I also brought you

121
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,330
a small gift.

122
00:06:38,370 --> 00:06:39,550
How many times have I told you

123
00:06:39,550 --> 00:06:40,470
not to bring gifts?

124
00:06:40,470 --> 00:06:41,930
You just...

125
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,210
A gold nugget.

126
00:06:55,590 --> 00:06:57,250
A friend dug it up in Xinjiang.

127
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:02,800
My friends and I

128
00:07:02,820 --> 00:07:03,330
registered a mining company

129
00:07:03,330 --> 00:07:04,740
over there.

130
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,750
It's a legitimate enterprise

131
00:07:06,750 --> 00:07:07,880
with mining rights.

132
00:07:08,660 --> 00:07:09,390
Next,

133
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:10,160
aren't we going

134
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,480
to develop Bolamula?

135
00:07:12,430 --> 00:07:14,360
Regarding the gold mining permit,

136
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,420
when the time comes,

137
00:07:16,420 --> 00:07:17,160
can you give us

138
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,620
priority consideration?

139
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,600
What makes you think

140
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,270
that development must be

141
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:31,980
destructive?

142
00:07:31,980 --> 00:07:33,580
When these mining companies

143
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:34,130
finish stripping the mine

144
00:07:34,130 --> 00:07:35,240
and skip town,

145
00:07:35,260 --> 00:07:36,930
what's left won't be wetlands—

146
00:07:36,930 --> 00:07:38,250
it'll just be a dead zone!

147
00:07:38,250 --> 00:07:38,920
Those in favor of submitting

148
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,680
the nature reserve application report,

149
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:42,080
please raise your hands.

150
00:07:45,390 --> 00:07:46,070
I believe

151
00:07:46,860 --> 00:07:47,430
we should not

152
00:07:47,430 --> 00:07:48,760
make this decision now.

153
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,810
On this trip to Beijing,

154
00:07:51,350 --> 00:07:53,750
besides giving lectures at universities,

155
00:07:53,810 --> 00:07:54,450
I'll meet with

156
00:07:54,450 --> 00:07:55,500
leaders and experts

157
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:57,130
from the Ministry of Forestry.

158
00:07:57,130 --> 00:07:58,210
I'll ask them for feedback

159
00:07:58,210 --> 00:07:58,980
on my report.

160
00:08:00,930 --> 00:08:02,150
We've waited 3 years.

161
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,540
We can also wait

162
00:08:05,510 --> 00:08:06,710
another month or two.

163
00:08:06,890 --> 00:08:07,830
Duojie and the Mountain Patrol

164
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:09,550
are getting a lot of attention.

165
00:08:09,550 --> 00:08:11,550
The publicity is gaining momentum.

166
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:14,340
The county government

167
00:08:14,550 --> 00:08:15,950
is increasingly in favor

168
00:08:16,150 --> 00:08:17,810
of establishing the reserve.

169
00:08:19,110 --> 00:08:20,840
I'm afraid there's very little

170
00:08:24,110 --> 00:08:25,770
I can do about this matter now.

171
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:28,600
Actually, some of the things

172
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,690
the Mountain Patrol does

173
00:08:29,690 --> 00:08:31,240
aren't exactly by the book.

174
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,600
Sometimes, letters from the public

175
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,700
come in handy.

176
00:08:41,750 --> 00:08:42,679
Don't you think?

177
00:08:53,340 --> 00:08:53,920
Feng.

178
00:08:56,460 --> 00:08:57,150
Actually, you can

179
00:08:57,150 --> 00:08:58,660
find Deputy County Mayor Duo,

180
00:08:58,660 --> 00:08:59,670
have a private chat,

181
00:08:59,670 --> 00:09:01,000
and try to persuade him.

182
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:02,720
Perhaps—

183
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,320
I know.

184
00:09:04,770 --> 00:09:05,900
I'll talk to him too.

185
00:09:50,030 --> 00:09:51,390
I've stalled him for a few days.

186
00:09:51,390 --> 00:09:53,470
After he comes back
and submits the report,

187
00:09:53,470 --> 00:09:54,460
establishing the reserve

188
00:09:54,460 --> 00:09:55,660
might be inevitable.

189
00:09:56,820 --> 00:09:57,150
You can

190
00:09:57,150 --> 00:09:58,260
take the time to talk to him

191
00:09:58,260 --> 00:09:59,240
when he returns.

192
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:09,890
This message

193
00:10:10,020 --> 00:10:11,270
was sent 17 years ago.

194
00:10:13,450 --> 00:10:14,850
You must have forgotten.

195
00:10:16,790 --> 00:10:17,390
I've already sent

196
00:10:17,390 --> 00:10:19,120
the flight information to you.

197
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:19,840
When are you planning

198
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:20,640
to talk to him?

199
00:10:23,130 --> 00:10:25,530
I'm already waiting for him
at the airport.

200
00:10:26,250 --> 00:10:27,460
You move fast.

201
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,210
Why the rush?

202
00:10:29,130 --> 00:10:29,790
After he returns,

203
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:31,410
he has to deal with team matters.

204
00:10:31,410 --> 00:10:32,550
I doubt he's in the mood to talk to you—

205
00:10:32,550 --> 00:10:33,550
County Mayor Lin,

206
00:10:34,130 --> 00:10:35,730
the Qima'er Gold Mine

207
00:10:35,870 --> 00:10:37,210
is actually mine.

208
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:42,940
Feng.

209
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:44,260
Feng, listen to me.

210
00:10:44,260 --> 00:10:44,960
Duojie responds to kindness,

211
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:45,940
not force.

212
00:10:46,170 --> 00:10:47,500
If you really can't reach an agreement,

213
00:10:47,500 --> 00:10:48,360
you can't force it.

214
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:50,090
Don't worry, County Mayor Lin.

215
00:10:50,220 --> 00:10:51,030
This time,

216
00:10:52,090 --> 00:10:53,620
we will reach an agreement.

217
00:10:53,930 --> 00:10:54,860
What do you mean?

218
00:10:55,850 --> 00:10:56,780
What do you mean?

219
00:10:57,510 --> 00:10:58,720
If we can't,

220
00:10:59,330 --> 00:11:01,050
he won't need to go back to Mazhi.

221
00:11:01,050 --> 00:11:02,450
What are you trying to do?

222
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,720
What are you trying to do?

223
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,370
Lin.

224
00:11:48,260 --> 00:11:49,260
All these years,

225
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:51,740
Jianshe going abroad,

226
00:11:52,180 --> 00:11:53,240
opening a company,

227
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:54,420
and buying a house,

228
00:11:55,220 --> 00:11:56,580
and the elderly getting sick,

229
00:11:56,580 --> 00:11:58,040
paying off those doctors—

230
00:11:59,040 --> 00:12:00,640
these didn't cost a fortune,

231
00:12:01,030 --> 00:12:02,760
but they weren't cheap either.

232
00:12:04,430 --> 00:12:05,830
If you don't help now,

233
00:12:06,650 --> 00:12:07,780
it wouldn't be fair.

234
00:12:12,530 --> 00:12:13,320
Fair?

235
00:12:16,030 --> 00:12:16,890
Back then,

236
00:12:16,940 --> 00:12:19,910
as to the approval
for the Duolong Mountain Gold Mine,

237
00:12:19,910 --> 00:12:21,050
it was Huang in the province

238
00:12:21,050 --> 00:12:22,310
who stamped it for you.

239
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,810
From Mazhi to Tianduo,

240
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:25,860
from a small mine

241
00:12:25,890 --> 00:12:27,510
to 7 large ones,

242
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:31,690
from coal mine integration

243
00:12:32,650 --> 00:12:34,510
to the mining ban and regreening,

244
00:12:35,050 --> 00:12:36,250
tell me, at which step

245
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,910
did I not push you up?

246
00:12:38,550 --> 00:12:39,880
Is what you're doing now

247
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:41,800
appropriate?

248
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:48,290
Only lovers care about appropriateness.

249
00:12:49,270 --> 00:12:50,530
I am a business person.

250
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:52,450
I only care if it's profitable.

251
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:55,570
The strong wind

252
00:12:55,570 --> 00:12:57,230
has already started blowing.

253
00:12:57,290 --> 00:12:58,570
Can that Swiss fresh air system

254
00:12:58,570 --> 00:13:00,440
you just installed at home

255
00:13:01,390 --> 00:13:02,170
filter out

256
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:03,530
the coal dust

257
00:13:03,550 --> 00:13:05,210
from 150 meters underground?

258
00:13:10,770 --> 00:13:12,120
I'll definitely stay in Tianduo

259
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:13,250
for a few more years.

260
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,460
The one anxious to retire

261
00:13:16,460 --> 00:13:17,750
isn't me anyway.

262
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:19,250
You can

263
00:13:20,830 --> 00:13:22,290
go back and think about it.

264
00:13:23,590 --> 00:13:24,730
Think carefully.

265
00:13:44,400 --> 00:13:45,430
As you just said,

266
00:13:47,630 --> 00:13:48,760
for the next 2 years,

267
00:13:51,530 --> 00:13:52,930
what is Xinhai's output?

268
00:13:53,310 --> 00:13:54,940
Five million tons a year.

269
00:13:58,690 --> 00:13:59,410
Feng.

270
00:14:05,730 --> 00:14:07,080
You're still

271
00:14:07,250 --> 00:14:09,470
that small merchant running a restaurant.

272
00:14:09,470 --> 00:14:10,300
After all these years,

273
00:14:10,300 --> 00:14:11,830
you haven't improved a bit.

274
00:14:14,330 --> 00:14:15,260
What do you mean?

275
00:14:17,160 --> 00:14:18,360
Since we're doing it,

276
00:14:20,170 --> 00:14:20,910
why can't the operation

277
00:14:20,910 --> 00:14:22,000
be bigger?

278
00:14:28,250 --> 00:14:29,460
I'll reach out to my friends

279
00:14:29,460 --> 00:14:30,390
in the province.

280
00:14:31,060 --> 00:14:33,060
I'll have them keep an eye out for me.

281
00:14:33,420 --> 00:14:34,820
If there's any movement,

282
00:14:35,160 --> 00:14:36,690
they'll tell me in advance.

283
00:14:37,410 --> 00:14:38,940
Speed things up on your end.

284
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:42,280
Once I step down next year,

285
00:14:42,280 --> 00:14:43,810
I'll find a way to go abroad.

286
00:14:44,290 --> 00:14:45,050
By then,

287
00:14:46,180 --> 00:14:47,840
however the sky changes here,

288
00:14:48,010 --> 00:14:49,870
it will have nothing to do with me.

289
00:14:50,750 --> 00:14:51,480
Understood,

290
00:14:51,950 --> 00:14:52,790
Mayor Lin.

291
00:14:53,670 --> 00:14:54,680
Duojie's body

292
00:14:54,700 --> 00:14:56,430
still hasn't been identified.

293
00:14:57,870 --> 00:14:58,470
Bai Ju

294
00:14:58,500 --> 00:15:00,300
will definitely not let this go.

295
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:02,890
As for her,

296
00:15:02,990 --> 00:15:04,520
Meng has been watching her.

297
00:15:05,460 --> 00:15:06,960
It's a society of law now.

298
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:07,940
Without evidence,

299
00:15:07,940 --> 00:15:09,190
as a little cop,

300
00:15:09,730 --> 00:15:11,940
she can't do anything,
no matter how hard she tries.

301
00:15:11,940 --> 00:15:12,720
That Reporter Shao

302
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:13,790
is the same.

303
00:15:14,380 --> 00:15:15,710
You don't need to worry.

304
00:15:16,340 --> 00:15:18,150
As for the Mountain Patrol,

305
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:21,130
they're just a bunch of idlers anyway.

306
00:15:21,590 --> 00:15:23,190
If they keep investigating,

307
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,800
we'll just wipe them all out.

308
00:15:26,250 --> 00:15:27,000
Don't worry.

309
00:15:27,910 --> 00:15:29,440
It'll look like an accident

310
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:31,090
with no traces left.

311
00:15:31,930 --> 00:15:33,170
What era is this?

312
00:15:35,270 --> 00:15:37,070
You still want to kill and fight?

313
00:15:37,870 --> 00:15:40,130
Do you want
to be a gangster all your life?

314
00:15:42,290 --> 00:15:43,650
If money can solve it,

315
00:15:45,260 --> 00:15:46,720
don't attract attention.

316
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:48,700
Okay.

317
00:15:50,040 --> 00:15:52,090
I promise not to cause you trouble.

318
00:15:58,410 --> 00:15:59,880
Don't push me.

319
00:15:59,910 --> 00:16:00,690
You're so strong.

320
00:16:00,690 --> 00:16:01,490
How did you get

321
00:16:01,500 --> 00:16:02,580
so strong?

322
00:16:05,660 --> 00:16:06,580
What are you doing?

323
00:16:06,580 --> 00:16:07,440
Put your hat on.

324
00:16:15,930 --> 00:16:17,410
Go inside. Don't look back.

325
00:16:17,410 --> 00:16:18,010
Go inside.

326
00:16:18,620 --> 00:16:19,270
Go inside.

327
00:16:37,980 --> 00:16:39,030
Reporter Shao.

328
00:16:40,190 --> 00:16:41,790
You really are a good father.

329
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:46,180
Not really.

330
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:48,010
Still learning.

331
00:16:49,790 --> 00:16:51,650
Your kid is in fifth grade, right?

332
00:16:52,120 --> 00:16:55,270
I heard you're trying to get her
into the provincial capital middle school.

333
00:16:55,270 --> 00:16:56,670
I have friends there too.

334
00:16:57,820 --> 00:16:58,700
If you need,

335
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,240
I can ask around for you.

336
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:00,890
No need.

337
00:17:03,010 --> 00:17:04,140
Thank you, Mr. Feng.

338
00:17:05,710 --> 00:17:07,099
I went to the provincial capital
last month

339
00:17:07,099 --> 00:17:09,160
and had a meal with your Chief Editor.

340
00:17:09,500 --> 00:17:10,900
We even talked about you.

341
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:12,589
We both think

342
00:17:12,730 --> 00:17:13,880
it's a pity

343
00:17:14,109 --> 00:17:14,900
that you're not moving up.

344
00:17:14,900 --> 00:17:15,920
Nothing to pity.

345
00:17:16,109 --> 00:17:17,420
Here, I can write reports

346
00:17:17,420 --> 00:17:18,910
and spend time with my family.

347
00:17:18,910 --> 00:17:19,400
It's better than

348
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:20,790
sitting in a big office.

349
00:17:21,609 --> 00:17:23,460
Mr. Feng, just say what you want.

350
00:17:23,609 --> 00:17:25,109
Stop beating around the bush.

351
00:17:25,109 --> 00:17:27,220
Xinhai is indeed mining privately.

352
00:17:29,290 --> 00:17:30,050
Two years.

353
00:17:30,590 --> 00:17:32,990
I'll mine for 2 more years
and then pull out.

354
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:37,980
Is that direct enough?

355
00:17:38,500 --> 00:17:39,240
What a pity.

356
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:41,680
You didn't record that in time.

357
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:42,240
Otherwise, it would be

358
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:44,240
strong evidence of illegal mining.

359
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:45,610
What do you want?

360
00:17:46,330 --> 00:17:47,790
One percent of the profits

361
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:49,440
from the next 2 years goes to you.

362
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:50,640
Your child's schooling

363
00:17:50,640 --> 00:17:51,640
and elderly care—

364
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:52,750
I can help you.

365
00:17:55,010 --> 00:17:55,740
How about it?

366
00:17:57,110 --> 00:17:57,930
As for Officer Bai,

367
00:17:57,930 --> 00:17:59,590
you find a way to persuade her.

368
00:17:59,770 --> 00:18:01,860
Actually, sometimes, a man

369
00:18:02,280 --> 00:18:03,520
should be decisive.

370
00:18:07,050 --> 00:18:07,720
It seems that you

371
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:08,850
still don't know me,

372
00:18:09,190 --> 00:18:11,050
and that you don't know my family.

373
00:18:11,630 --> 00:18:13,690
The women are in charge in our family.

374
00:18:14,560 --> 00:18:15,820
I really didn't expect

375
00:18:16,290 --> 00:18:18,490
Tianduo's top entrepreneur

376
00:18:18,510 --> 00:18:19,840
to be like this.

377
00:18:20,410 --> 00:18:21,250
Like what?

378
00:18:24,360 --> 00:18:26,890
Carrying the banner
of economic development

379
00:18:27,410 --> 00:18:29,410
while destroying the environment.

380
00:18:29,970 --> 00:18:31,240
Overdrawing the future

381
00:18:31,240 --> 00:18:33,070
to satisfy present selfish desires.

382
00:18:33,070 --> 00:18:34,070
Selfish desires?

383
00:18:35,710 --> 00:18:37,440
Isn't that too narrow-minded?

384
00:18:38,330 --> 00:18:38,940
Do you know

385
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:40,250
what this place was like

386
00:18:40,250 --> 00:18:41,010
20 years ago?

387
00:18:42,250 --> 00:18:44,200
It was slightly better than Mazhi County.

388
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:45,930
But how much better could it be?

389
00:18:46,350 --> 00:18:48,090
Tianduo's best hotel

390
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:50,070
couldn't even provide electricity all day.

391
00:18:50,070 --> 00:18:50,740
In winter,

392
00:18:50,770 --> 00:18:51,980
guests had to

393
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,930
light their own stoves for warmth.

394
00:18:54,990 --> 00:18:56,110
And 20 years later?

395
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:57,270
Here, we built

396
00:18:57,270 --> 00:18:59,070
five-star hotels

397
00:18:59,550 --> 00:19:00,820
and stadiums.

398
00:19:02,290 --> 00:19:03,480
The herdsmen here

399
00:19:03,650 --> 00:19:04,300
no longer

400
00:19:04,330 --> 00:19:05,570
herd on horseback

401
00:19:05,590 --> 00:19:06,960
like their fathers.

402
00:19:07,790 --> 00:19:09,470
When they ride motorcycles

403
00:19:09,570 --> 00:19:10,640
and drive cars,

404
00:19:11,250 --> 00:19:11,980
do you think they want

405
00:19:11,980 --> 00:19:13,200
to get back on a horse?

406
00:19:13,730 --> 00:19:14,750
Will Zhacuo?

407
00:19:16,650 --> 00:19:17,680
I'm sorry.

408
00:19:18,280 --> 00:19:19,500
It's impossible.

409
00:19:19,900 --> 00:19:21,250
This is human nature.

410
00:19:21,940 --> 00:19:23,640
An insatiable nature.

411
00:19:24,350 --> 00:19:25,500
A nature that allows you

412
00:19:25,500 --> 00:19:26,780
to discard

413
00:19:26,810 --> 00:19:28,410
your so-called traditions.

414
00:19:29,610 --> 00:19:31,410
And whoever grasps this nature

415
00:19:32,850 --> 00:19:35,010
wins the era.

416
00:19:42,660 --> 00:19:44,000
Then let me tell you something.

417
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:44,810
You can use your connections

418
00:19:44,810 --> 00:19:45,540
to silence me

419
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:46,930
and delete my articles.

420
00:19:47,030 --> 00:19:47,920
But don't stand here

421
00:19:47,920 --> 00:19:49,680
twisting facts
and confusing right and wrong,

422
00:19:49,680 --> 00:19:50,700
playing the savior

423
00:19:50,700 --> 00:19:52,230
while poisoning this city.

424
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:54,010
Economic development
and environmental protection

425
00:19:54,010 --> 00:19:55,540
have never been opposites.

426
00:19:55,870 --> 00:19:56,380
No matter

427
00:19:56,380 --> 00:19:58,050
how sanctimonious you act,

428
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:01,810
your original sin

429
00:20:02,600 --> 00:20:03,800
can't be washed away.

430
00:20:06,610 --> 00:20:08,390
Just like that photo you took,

431
00:20:09,610 --> 00:20:10,850
no matter how beautiful
or spectacular it is,

432
00:20:10,850 --> 00:20:11,640
you know

433
00:20:11,660 --> 00:20:12,770
how you took it,

434
00:20:12,960 --> 00:20:14,420
so does the snow mountain.

435
00:20:14,590 --> 00:20:16,570
Those dirty things you did

436
00:20:17,360 --> 00:20:19,020
will be known sooner or later.

437
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,620
Wonderful.

438
00:20:23,380 --> 00:20:25,430
Well said.

439
00:20:26,330 --> 00:20:27,960
As expected of Reporter Shao.

440
00:20:27,960 --> 00:20:29,620
No wonder you can write so many

441
00:20:29,660 --> 00:20:30,790
brilliant reports.

442
00:20:35,660 --> 00:20:36,640
As far as I know,

443
00:20:37,460 --> 00:20:38,660
Officer Bai's family

444
00:20:38,660 --> 00:20:40,790
is doing business with Xinhai, right?

445
00:20:45,640 --> 00:20:47,040
Will they think as you do?

446
00:22:06,110 --> 00:22:07,840
What are you doing here? Leave!

447
00:22:08,050 --> 00:22:08,790
Zhacuo.

448
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:11,200
Let's talk.

449
00:22:11,770 --> 00:22:13,690
I have nothing to talk to you about.

450
00:22:13,690 --> 00:22:14,270
Leave!

451
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:30,250
Do you have a death wish?

452
00:22:46,730 --> 00:22:47,930
Don't you know

453
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:49,810
what kind of person Meng Yaohui is?

454
00:22:49,810 --> 00:22:50,540
He came to you,

455
00:22:50,540 --> 00:22:51,890
and you should've refused him directly.

456
00:22:51,890 --> 00:22:53,140
Why are you discussing it with us?

457
00:22:53,140 --> 00:22:54,740
There's nothing to discuss.

458
00:22:55,270 --> 00:22:56,930
Since the coal mine is closed,

459
00:22:57,400 --> 00:22:58,860
I can't cash out my shares.

460
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:01,000
Meng said

461
00:23:01,070 --> 00:23:01,810
he could pay a high price

462
00:23:01,810 --> 00:23:02,640
for my shares.

463
00:23:03,030 --> 00:23:04,010
Shares?

464
00:23:04,670 --> 00:23:05,360
Why don't you just

465
00:23:05,360 --> 00:23:06,560
sell yourself to him?

466
00:23:10,280 --> 00:23:11,460
But I really am

467
00:23:11,610 --> 00:23:12,400
under a lot of pressure

468
00:23:12,400 --> 00:23:13,900
because of the mortgage.

469
00:23:14,270 --> 00:23:16,730
My wife even borrowed money
from her family.

470
00:23:17,070 --> 00:23:17,650
Everyone has a family

471
00:23:17,650 --> 00:23:18,580
to feed now.

472
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:20,250
We have to make a living.

473
00:23:20,250 --> 00:23:21,140
Look at Bai.

474
00:23:21,680 --> 00:23:22,660
He's on leave!

475
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:24,700
If you want to talk about pressure,

476
00:23:24,700 --> 00:23:26,160
who isn't under pressure?

477
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:27,590
I-I...

478
00:23:27,930 --> 00:23:28,570
Aren't we all

479
00:23:28,570 --> 00:23:29,030
doing this

480
00:23:29,030 --> 00:23:29,700
under pressure?

481
00:23:29,700 --> 00:23:30,410
Yeah, yeah.

482
00:23:30,440 --> 00:23:31,430
Zhacuo, listen to me.

483
00:23:31,430 --> 00:23:32,290
Think about it.

484
00:23:32,350 --> 00:23:34,010
The Mountain Patrol
had it worse back then,

485
00:23:34,010 --> 00:23:35,810
but we got through it, didn't we?

486
00:23:35,940 --> 00:23:37,140
I don't get it anyway.

487
00:23:37,610 --> 00:23:38,510
Is there any point

488
00:23:38,510 --> 00:23:39,380
investigating Xinhai now?

489
00:23:39,380 --> 00:23:40,860
Of course there's a point.

490
00:23:42,010 --> 00:23:43,250
I think the Xinhai case

491
00:23:43,250 --> 00:23:44,110
and the Captain's case

492
00:23:44,110 --> 00:23:45,410
are the same thing.

493
00:23:45,880 --> 00:23:47,610
You're still bringing that up?

494
00:23:47,960 --> 00:23:48,440
In the beginning,

495
00:23:48,440 --> 00:23:50,030
wasn't it because we thought

496
00:23:50,030 --> 00:23:51,250
you could solve the Captain's case

497
00:23:51,250 --> 00:23:52,000
that everyone followed you

498
00:23:52,000 --> 00:23:53,030
to do this?

499
00:23:53,140 --> 00:23:54,070
But now look,

500
00:23:54,180 --> 00:23:55,310
we've found nothing

501
00:23:55,830 --> 00:23:56,850
and got into a lot of trouble.

502
00:23:56,850 --> 00:23:57,820
You need to speak

503
00:23:57,850 --> 00:23:58,940
with a conscience.

504
00:23:59,420 --> 00:24:00,940
What trouble did you get into?

505
00:24:00,940 --> 00:24:02,000
Even if we didn't investigate Xinhai,

506
00:24:02,000 --> 00:24:02,720
your

507
00:24:02,750 --> 00:24:03,720
dry shares in the coal mining company

508
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:04,980
would still be stuck.

509
00:24:05,530 --> 00:24:06,590
Now, you drive a nice car

510
00:24:06,590 --> 00:24:07,290
and live in a nice house.

511
00:24:07,290 --> 00:24:08,350
You've had it too good.

512
00:24:08,350 --> 00:24:09,350
I think you've forgotten

513
00:24:09,350 --> 00:24:09,900
whose side

514
00:24:09,900 --> 00:24:10,570
you're on.

515
00:24:10,590 --> 00:24:11,070
You...

516
00:24:11,110 --> 00:24:12,050
-Shao Yunfei.
-To be blunt,

517
00:24:12,050 --> 00:24:12,850
now that Meng Yaohui

518
00:24:12,850 --> 00:24:13,680
offers you some benefits,

519
00:24:13,680 --> 00:24:14,670
you've wavered.

520
00:24:15,000 --> 00:24:16,000
You can't convince us,

521
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:17,030
so you change the subject,

522
00:24:17,030 --> 00:24:18,160
saying the investigation is troublesome

523
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:18,680
and pointless.

524
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:19,180
Actually,

525
00:24:19,180 --> 00:24:20,070
it's just that you can't get benefits
anymore.

526
00:24:20,070 --> 00:24:20,290
Enough.

527
00:24:20,290 --> 00:24:21,250
You're angry out of embarrassment.

528
00:24:21,250 --> 00:24:22,310
But let me tell you,

529
00:24:22,770 --> 00:24:24,430
taking it out on us won't help.

530
00:24:24,830 --> 00:24:25,550
Anger is just

531
00:24:25,550 --> 00:24:26,420
a sign of incompetence.

532
00:24:26,420 --> 00:24:27,570
Do it if you can.

533
00:24:27,590 --> 00:24:28,270
If you don't want to,

534
00:24:28,270 --> 00:24:28,960
then quit.

535
00:24:29,050 --> 00:24:29,920
We don't need you.

536
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:31,090
I'll teach you a lesson for your father.

537
00:24:31,090 --> 00:24:31,570
Fine.

538
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:32,940
You say that every time.

539
00:24:32,940 --> 00:24:33,360
Isn't it annoying?

540
00:24:33,360 --> 00:24:34,070
Shao Yunfei.

541
00:24:34,070 --> 00:24:36,400
"I'll teach you a lesson for your father."

542
00:24:36,920 --> 00:24:37,500
Let go!

543
00:24:37,610 --> 00:24:38,610
What are you doing?

544
00:24:38,610 --> 00:24:39,400
Stop fighting!

545
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:39,980
Stop fighting!

546
00:24:39,980 --> 00:24:40,720
Let go!

547
00:24:40,920 --> 00:24:41,530
Let go!

548
00:24:41,550 --> 00:24:42,410
Stop fighting!

549
00:24:42,650 --> 00:24:43,510
Stop fighting!

550
00:24:48,660 --> 00:24:50,780
It's not just about investigating
illegal coal trafficking

551
00:24:50,780 --> 00:24:52,150
and illegal mining.

552
00:24:52,660 --> 00:24:53,520
These are just

553
00:24:53,550 --> 00:24:54,810
speculations for now,

554
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:56,830
but contraband was found

555
00:24:56,930 --> 00:24:58,070
in Han's dorm,

556
00:24:58,640 --> 00:25:00,370
and Meng Yaohui came to give Zhacuo

557
00:25:00,370 --> 00:25:01,570
share compensation,

558
00:25:01,880 --> 00:25:02,440
trying to find out

559
00:25:02,440 --> 00:25:03,960
what exactly I've uncovered.

560
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:04,480
What do you think

561
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,940
they are so nervous about?

562
00:25:08,930 --> 00:25:10,350
This Zhacuo, really,

563
00:25:11,290 --> 00:25:12,720
is too heavy-handed.

564
00:25:13,810 --> 00:25:15,490
He actually held back.

565
00:25:16,100 --> 00:25:18,560
Otherwise,
I'd be in an ambulance right now.

566
00:25:28,860 --> 00:25:30,410
What's wrong with your back?

567
00:25:30,410 --> 00:25:30,980
I'm fine.

568
00:25:33,810 --> 00:25:35,340
It's been like this lately.

569
00:25:39,600 --> 00:25:40,860
My mom has a set of

570
00:25:40,880 --> 00:25:42,010
moxibustion tools.

571
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:45,090
But she's on the night shift today,

572
00:25:45,110 --> 00:25:46,310
and she won't be back.

573
00:25:48,100 --> 00:25:49,500
I'll go see her tomorrow.

574
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:50,560
It's okay.

575
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:52,250
I'll figure it out when we get back

576
00:25:52,250 --> 00:25:53,310
and try to help you.

577
00:25:54,510 --> 00:25:55,440
I sprained my back last time

578
00:25:55,440 --> 00:25:56,830
and have some plasters left.

579
00:25:56,830 --> 00:25:58,230
I'll put one on you later.

580
00:26:00,420 --> 00:26:01,220
Do you want it?

581
00:26:01,310 --> 00:26:01,640
Yes.

582
00:26:01,980 --> 00:26:02,810
Yes, yes.

583
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:04,380
Yes.

584
00:26:18,420 --> 00:26:19,030
Mom.

585
00:26:19,380 --> 00:26:20,360
You're all here.

586
00:26:21,110 --> 00:26:22,110
You didn't go to your night shift?

587
00:26:22,110 --> 00:26:23,770
Shao Yunfei just sprained his back.

588
00:26:23,770 --> 00:26:25,500
Where is your moxibustion kit?

589
00:26:30,610 --> 00:26:32,010
You should go back first.

590
00:26:32,040 --> 00:26:34,240
We have some family matters to discuss.

591
00:26:35,710 --> 00:26:36,510
What's wrong?

592
00:26:39,650 --> 00:26:40,500
Mr. Meng,

593
00:26:40,590 --> 00:26:41,920
there must be a mistake.

594
00:26:42,050 --> 00:26:42,840
Our grass seeds

595
00:26:42,840 --> 00:26:43,400
went through

596
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:44,980
strict selection and control.

597
00:26:44,980 --> 00:26:46,400
There can't be any problems.

598
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:47,730
And the previous scheduled inspections

599
00:26:47,730 --> 00:26:48,710
were all normal.

600
00:26:49,070 --> 00:26:49,740
It was clearly

601
00:26:49,740 --> 00:26:50,610
growing well,

602
00:26:50,720 --> 00:26:52,380
then suddenly turned yellow.

603
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:54,440
This is definitely not normal.

604
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:56,590
The inspection team
happened to be visiting at the time.

605
00:26:56,590 --> 00:26:57,270
They immediately

606
00:26:57,270 --> 00:26:58,670
took photos as evidence.

607
00:26:58,900 --> 00:27:00,690
The company takes this very seriously

608
00:27:00,690 --> 00:27:02,290
and wants a re-examination.

609
00:27:02,660 --> 00:27:04,790
We need to take samples from the field.

610
00:27:05,270 --> 00:27:07,070
If you pass the re-examination,

611
00:27:07,070 --> 00:27:08,200
you can resume work.

612
00:27:11,740 --> 00:27:12,900
But if you don't,

613
00:27:13,380 --> 00:27:14,250
and your grass seeds

614
00:27:14,250 --> 00:27:15,970
are confirmed to be adulterated,

615
00:27:15,970 --> 00:27:17,750
you will be liable for damages.

616
00:27:18,230 --> 00:27:19,640
This will also involve

617
00:27:19,770 --> 00:27:20,970
a breach of contract.

618
00:27:21,110 --> 00:27:22,610
How can this
be considered a breach of contract?

619
00:27:22,610 --> 00:27:23,260
At most,

620
00:27:23,290 --> 00:27:24,850
it's just substandard work.

621
00:27:24,850 --> 00:27:25,220
Then...

622
00:27:25,220 --> 00:27:26,590
we'll just redo it.

623
00:27:26,880 --> 00:27:29,480
If the grass seeds
are found to be adulterated,

624
00:27:29,700 --> 00:27:31,960
then Changqing commits contract fraud.

625
00:27:32,140 --> 00:27:33,800
As the legal representative,

626
00:27:33,870 --> 00:27:34,500
you will have to bear

627
00:27:34,500 --> 00:27:36,530
the corresponding legal responsibilities.

628
00:27:36,530 --> 00:27:37,460
Is that clear?

629
00:27:39,170 --> 00:27:40,770
This is absolutely lawless.

630
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:41,700
Meng Yaohui

631
00:27:41,700 --> 00:27:42,850
is threatening you.

632
00:27:43,130 --> 00:27:44,480
He's threatening us.

633
00:27:45,150 --> 00:27:45,940
Bai Ju,

634
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:47,220
aren't you and Meng Yaohui

635
00:27:47,220 --> 00:27:48,480
on pretty good terms?

636
00:27:48,800 --> 00:27:49,170
Mom,

637
00:27:49,190 --> 00:27:50,120
stay out of this.

638
00:27:50,140 --> 00:27:50,970
You don't understand.

639
00:27:50,970 --> 00:27:52,500
I don't understand either.

640
00:27:52,700 --> 00:27:53,400
I only found out

641
00:27:53,400 --> 00:27:54,660
today.

642
00:27:54,750 --> 00:27:55,200
Earlier,

643
00:27:55,200 --> 00:27:56,160
someone reported to the inspection team

644
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:57,750
about Xinhai's illegal mining.

645
00:27:57,750 --> 00:27:59,010
It was you, wasn't it?

646
00:28:03,230 --> 00:28:05,090
So that's where the problem lies.

647
00:28:05,360 --> 00:28:06,700
Serves you right.

648
00:28:07,110 --> 00:28:07,830
Bai Ji.

649
00:28:09,060 --> 00:28:10,190
What are you saying?

650
00:28:10,610 --> 00:28:11,720
Bai Ji, what do you mean?

651
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:12,660
What do I mean?

652
00:28:13,000 --> 00:28:13,520
I deserve it

653
00:28:13,520 --> 00:28:14,780
when he turned against me!

654
00:28:14,780 --> 00:28:16,180
I deserve to go bankrupt!

655
00:28:16,180 --> 00:28:17,440
I deserve to go to jail!

656
00:28:20,220 --> 00:28:20,940
Behind my back,

657
00:28:20,940 --> 00:28:21,690
however you mess with Xinhai,

658
00:28:21,690 --> 00:28:22,740
I don't care!

659
00:28:22,940 --> 00:28:24,110
But can't you think about me?

660
00:28:24,110 --> 00:28:25,380
Think about Chun?

661
00:28:26,160 --> 00:28:27,420
I warned you back then.

662
00:28:28,010 --> 00:28:29,640
You said Chun was in charge too,

663
00:28:29,640 --> 00:28:30,990
so I kept my mouth shut.

664
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:31,610
Besides,

665
00:28:31,610 --> 00:28:32,870
with Uncle Lin's recommendation,

666
00:28:32,870 --> 00:28:34,270
I didn't think much of it.

667
00:28:34,570 --> 00:28:35,900
As for reporting Xinhai

668
00:28:36,090 --> 00:28:37,200
and alerting the enemy,

669
00:28:37,200 --> 00:28:38,510
I only found out later.

670
00:28:38,600 --> 00:28:40,310
Of course you didn't have to think much.

671
00:28:40,310 --> 00:28:42,010
You didn't pay a cent.

672
00:28:42,330 --> 00:28:43,310
Chun, Shao,

673
00:28:43,340 --> 00:28:43,950
Mom, and I

674
00:28:44,060 --> 00:28:45,350
threw all our money in.

675
00:28:45,560 --> 00:28:46,270
You only care

676
00:28:46,270 --> 00:28:47,900
about yourself!

677
00:28:48,080 --> 00:28:50,080
Who do you care about in this family?

678
00:28:50,500 --> 00:28:50,750
Bai Ji,

679
00:28:50,750 --> 00:28:52,210
how can you talk like that?

680
00:28:53,940 --> 00:28:54,960
I really don't understand.

681
00:28:54,960 --> 00:28:56,330
Why are you so afraid?

682
00:28:56,700 --> 00:28:57,770
We have nothing to hide.

683
00:28:57,770 --> 00:28:59,000
Xinhai is the one breaking the law.

684
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:00,340
We didn't do anything wrong.

685
00:29:00,340 --> 00:29:01,000
I don't understand

686
00:29:01,000 --> 00:29:02,460
what you're afraid of!

687
00:29:02,550 --> 00:29:03,610
What am I afraid of?

688
00:29:03,980 --> 00:29:04,480
Ju,

689
00:29:04,730 --> 00:29:05,330
I don't know

690
00:29:05,330 --> 00:29:06,770
if you're actually stupid

691
00:29:06,770 --> 00:29:07,970
or just playing dumb.

692
00:29:08,270 --> 00:29:10,030
You guys kept messing with Xinhai.

693
00:29:10,030 --> 00:29:11,270
It even went to the inspection team.

694
00:29:11,270 --> 00:29:12,530
And what is the result?

695
00:29:12,900 --> 00:29:14,300
The regreening project.

696
00:29:14,480 --> 00:29:15,460
That's a huge deal!

697
00:29:15,460 --> 00:29:16,680
Meng Yaohui dared to use this

698
00:29:16,680 --> 00:29:17,650
to threaten me!

699
00:29:17,770 --> 00:29:18,730
Why?

700
00:29:19,460 --> 00:29:20,610
Because in Tianduo,

701
00:29:21,050 --> 00:29:21,960
Xinhai

702
00:29:22,140 --> 00:29:23,710
controls everything!

703
00:29:23,990 --> 00:29:25,900
-Do I have to spell it out for you?
-Let me tell you, Bai Ji!

704
00:29:25,900 --> 00:29:26,920
They can't do it!

705
00:29:26,940 --> 00:29:28,280
What makes you so sure?

706
00:29:29,010 --> 00:29:29,290
When that happens,

707
00:29:29,290 --> 00:29:30,350
can you protect me?

708
00:29:30,420 --> 00:29:31,070
Can you protect Chun?

709
00:29:31,070 --> 00:29:32,670
Can you protect Mom and Shao?

710
00:29:33,010 --> 00:29:34,010
All these years,

711
00:29:34,140 --> 00:29:34,940
Bai Ju,

712
00:29:35,350 --> 00:29:36,380
have you even figured out

713
00:29:36,380 --> 00:29:37,590
your own mess?

714
00:29:37,850 --> 00:29:38,400
Have you figured out

715
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:39,250
the Duojie case?

716
00:29:39,250 --> 00:29:39,810
Bai Ji!

717
00:29:48,520 --> 00:29:49,240
Justice...

718
00:29:51,240 --> 00:29:52,220
Justice might be late.

719
00:29:52,220 --> 00:29:52,850
Don't give me

720
00:29:52,850 --> 00:29:53,790
your empty talk.

721
00:29:53,820 --> 00:29:54,600
Late?

722
00:29:54,790 --> 00:29:55,510
Fine.

723
00:29:56,510 --> 00:29:56,980
Then how long

724
00:29:56,980 --> 00:29:57,670
will we wait

725
00:29:57,700 --> 00:29:58,850
for it to arrive?

726
00:29:59,610 --> 00:30:01,270
Wait until we lose everything

727
00:30:01,270 --> 00:30:02,450
and the family is destroyed?

728
00:30:02,450 --> 00:30:03,850
Will it be of any use then?

729
00:30:04,140 --> 00:30:04,770
Bai Ji.

730
00:30:06,270 --> 00:30:06,960
How can you...

731
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:07,570
Ju.

732
00:30:07,920 --> 00:30:08,550
Ju, Ju.

733
00:30:08,860 --> 00:30:10,700
Let me just ask you one thing.

734
00:30:11,290 --> 00:30:12,750
For the sake of our family,

735
00:30:13,700 --> 00:30:15,370
can you just stop with the Xinhai business

736
00:30:15,370 --> 00:30:17,140
for now?

737
00:30:17,290 --> 00:30:17,850
I'm not asking you

738
00:30:17,850 --> 00:30:19,180
to let it go completely.

739
00:30:20,830 --> 00:30:21,960
I'm begging you.

740
00:30:22,380 --> 00:30:23,460
I'm begging you.

741
00:30:23,700 --> 00:30:24,850
For the family,

742
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:27,010
can you just pause

743
00:30:27,240 --> 00:30:28,240
for a bit?

744
00:30:36,710 --> 00:30:37,860
I never thought...

745
00:30:40,210 --> 00:30:41,870
I never thought my own brother

746
00:30:42,330 --> 00:30:43,600
could say such things.

747
00:30:46,220 --> 00:30:48,440
You're not my biological sister anyway.

748
00:30:48,440 --> 00:30:49,740
Bai Ji, what are you saying?

749
00:30:49,740 --> 00:30:50,730
Did I say something wrong?

750
00:30:50,730 --> 00:30:52,790
In the end, we're not blood-related!

751
00:30:52,900 --> 00:30:53,650
-Mom!
-Stop!

752
00:30:53,870 --> 00:30:54,850
Did I say something wrong?

753
00:30:54,850 --> 00:30:55,270
Mom, Mom, Mom!

754
00:30:55,270 --> 00:30:56,530
Do we owe her anything?

755
00:30:56,550 --> 00:30:57,130
Enough! Shut your mouth!

756
00:30:57,130 --> 00:30:57,980
She can't treat us like this!

757
00:30:57,980 --> 00:30:58,910
Get out! Get out!

758
00:30:59,230 --> 00:31:00,040
I owe you!

759
00:31:00,070 --> 00:31:00,460
What nonsense are you spouting?

760
00:31:00,460 --> 00:31:01,050
You treat us like this!

761
00:31:01,050 --> 00:31:01,830
Shut up!

762
00:31:01,940 --> 00:31:03,940
Bai Ju, your personality...

763
00:31:17,610 --> 00:31:19,070
It's just like Wang Xia's.

764
00:31:25,670 --> 00:31:26,480
That day,

765
00:31:27,290 --> 00:31:29,290
the forecast predicted a blizzard.

766
00:31:30,900 --> 00:31:31,650
I told her

767
00:31:31,680 --> 00:31:33,010
not to go on your rounds.

768
00:31:34,920 --> 00:31:36,180
The township she was going to

769
00:31:36,180 --> 00:31:37,400
was too far.

770
00:31:39,540 --> 00:31:41,200
Blizzards would come without warning.

771
00:31:41,200 --> 00:31:42,930
They wouldn't wait for anyone.

772
00:31:45,010 --> 00:31:45,980
But she said

773
00:31:46,430 --> 00:31:48,630
patients wouldn't wait for you either.

774
00:31:51,960 --> 00:31:53,700
Later, Yang went with her.

775
00:32:00,220 --> 00:32:02,530
She was so stubborn.

776
00:32:03,390 --> 00:32:04,790
Once her mind was set on something,

777
00:32:04,790 --> 00:32:06,550
everything else came second.

778
00:32:11,530 --> 00:32:13,330
You're just like her in that way.

779
00:32:29,470 --> 00:32:30,460
But from the moment

780
00:32:30,460 --> 00:32:31,520
I brought you home,

781
00:32:31,880 --> 00:32:33,400
you became my child.

782
00:32:34,830 --> 00:32:36,050
We're kin.

783
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:40,320
Your brother
was just saying that out of anger.

784
00:32:41,580 --> 00:32:42,250
I know you...

785
00:32:42,250 --> 00:32:43,030
Mom, I know.

786
00:32:47,290 --> 00:32:48,420
I'm not mad at him.

787
00:32:54,390 --> 00:32:55,610
You're a good kid.

788
00:32:58,610 --> 00:33:00,670
But I'm afraid to even think about it.

789
00:33:01,250 --> 00:33:01,880
If Bai Ji

790
00:33:01,900 --> 00:33:03,270
really goes that far...

791
00:33:08,230 --> 00:33:09,810
It isn't easy for him

792
00:33:09,840 --> 00:33:11,320
to get where he is today.

793
00:33:12,570 --> 00:33:14,100
And regarding this matter,

794
00:33:16,310 --> 00:33:17,090
when it comes down to it,

795
00:33:17,090 --> 00:33:18,690
he didn't do anything wrong.

796
00:33:20,360 --> 00:33:21,810
Maybe these years,

797
00:33:22,140 --> 00:33:23,840
we've had it too good,

798
00:33:25,560 --> 00:33:26,890
and we forgot one thing.

799
00:33:28,850 --> 00:33:29,430
We

800
00:33:29,460 --> 00:33:30,920
can lose everything else,

801
00:33:32,330 --> 00:33:33,260
but we can't lose

802
00:33:33,280 --> 00:33:35,370
our integrity.

803
00:33:42,330 --> 00:33:42,810
Mom.

804
00:33:44,180 --> 00:33:44,920
But I can't bring myself

805
00:33:44,920 --> 00:33:45,760
to say this

806
00:33:45,790 --> 00:33:47,250
to Bai Ji's face.

807
00:33:53,140 --> 00:33:53,870
I don't know

808
00:33:53,900 --> 00:33:55,200
what to do anymore.

809
00:34:41,110 --> 00:34:42,440
Mom told me everything.

810
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:46,560
She asked me to come check on you.

811
00:34:47,960 --> 00:34:48,880
She said...

812
00:34:51,909 --> 00:34:53,710
she loves you both equally.

813
00:34:59,900 --> 00:35:00,760
Bai Ju...

814
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:02,050
If we weren't kin,

815
00:35:02,070 --> 00:35:03,400
things would be easier.

816
00:35:05,140 --> 00:35:06,390
Just for the truth,

817
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:10,880
do I really have to sacrifice Bai Ji,

818
00:35:12,210 --> 00:35:13,130
Mom,

819
00:35:15,680 --> 00:35:16,930
and the whole family?

820
00:35:19,450 --> 00:35:20,780
Why should they

821
00:35:23,500 --> 00:35:24,940
bear this with me?

822
00:35:29,210 --> 00:35:30,390
If back then,

823
00:35:33,400 --> 00:35:34,720
Mom hadn't saved me,

824
00:35:37,130 --> 00:35:37,570
and I wasn't

825
00:35:37,570 --> 00:35:38,830
part of this family...

826
00:35:42,200 --> 00:35:43,400
I'm a police officer.

827
00:35:46,400 --> 00:35:47,980
But I'm also a daughter,

828
00:35:49,420 --> 00:35:51,000
a big sister,

829
00:35:51,820 --> 00:35:52,750
a little sister,

830
00:35:55,030 --> 00:35:56,180
and a mother.

831
00:36:02,250 --> 00:36:04,310
I really don't blame Bai Ji this time.

832
00:36:07,320 --> 00:36:09,120
His worries are actually valid.

833
00:36:12,120 --> 00:36:13,850
First, it is Zhacuo and others,

834
00:36:15,730 --> 00:36:16,890
then it is Bai Ji.

835
00:36:18,560 --> 00:36:20,920
Meng Yaohui
dared to bring it into the open this time,

836
00:36:20,920 --> 00:36:23,260
threatening us
with the regreening project.

837
00:36:23,260 --> 00:36:24,790
This is just the first step.

838
00:36:30,990 --> 00:36:31,920
What comes next?

839
00:36:35,530 --> 00:36:36,460
What should I do?

840
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:41,760
You won't stop.

841
00:36:43,110 --> 00:36:44,240
When the time comes,

842
00:36:46,130 --> 00:36:47,590
just keep moving forward.

843
00:36:48,530 --> 00:36:49,460
Don't be afraid.

844
00:36:51,990 --> 00:36:53,650
I'll stay and watch the house.

845
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:58,050
This home

846
00:37:00,640 --> 00:37:01,660
is my home too.

847
00:37:25,600 --> 00:37:27,270
So I can only count on you

848
00:37:28,360 --> 00:37:30,490
when it's absolutely necessary, huh?

849
00:37:33,620 --> 00:37:34,950
You're feeling better.

850
00:37:36,050 --> 00:37:36,840
What?

851
00:37:37,420 --> 00:37:39,620
You've got the energy to tease me again.

852
00:37:41,710 --> 00:37:42,910
But you've forgotten

853
00:37:43,320 --> 00:37:44,530
what I said before.

854
00:37:45,650 --> 00:37:47,260
I won't suddenly leave.

855
00:37:49,990 --> 00:37:51,450
I'll only suddenly appear

856
00:37:52,730 --> 00:37:54,210
when you need me.

857
00:38:00,370 --> 00:38:01,970
I lost the Captain back then.

858
00:38:02,910 --> 00:38:03,750
Now, I can't lose

859
00:38:03,750 --> 00:38:04,980
my brother too.

860
00:38:49,920 --> 00:38:50,920
At Xinhai Coal Mine in our city,

861
00:38:50,920 --> 00:38:52,530
a major coal theft occurred.

862
00:38:52,550 --> 00:38:53,010
The involved

863
00:38:53,010 --> 00:38:54,010
field dispatcher

864
00:38:54,010 --> 00:38:54,730
and security guard

865
00:38:54,730 --> 00:38:56,590
are under police investigation.

866
00:38:57,380 --> 00:38:58,320
Xinhai has cooperated

867
00:38:58,320 --> 00:38:59,000
with the public security department

868
00:38:59,000 --> 00:39:00,340
to form a special investigation team.

869
00:39:00,340 --> 00:39:01,130
They are comprehensively reviewing

870
00:39:01,130 --> 00:39:02,690
the coal management process,

871
00:39:02,690 --> 00:39:03,340
launching full background checks

872
00:39:03,340 --> 00:39:04,890
on involved positions

873
00:39:04,920 --> 00:39:06,870
and retracing operational procedures.

874
00:39:06,870 --> 00:39:07,310
Next,

875
00:39:07,340 --> 00:39:08,960
we will upgrade the monitoring system.

876
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:10,320
For coal transportation

877
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:11,360
and storage,

878
00:39:11,380 --> 00:39:13,210
we will implement
full-process supervision,

879
00:39:13,210 --> 00:39:14,610
ensuring every ton of coal

880
00:39:14,610 --> 00:39:15,650
is traceable to its source,

881
00:39:15,650 --> 00:39:17,910
and that its destination is controlled.

882
00:39:33,510 --> 00:39:34,310
You're awake.

883
00:39:34,550 --> 00:39:35,190
Here, perfect timing.

